  "name": "Kanatlı Buz Mantarı",
  "desc": "<p>A mimetic life form made out of spores that has extreme adaptability.</p><p>Going well past mere appearances, this being even imitates the habits of birds. When it flies about, it will scatter icy flowers in its wake. These crystal cores, too, are spores.</p><p>This creature has a position of command amongst colonies of fungal beasts and exhibits heightened intelligence to match.</p>",
